<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM4.1.1">
<l>katirā yiramiravi kalanterit tālotta nīḷmuṭiyaṉ</l>
<l>etiril perumai yirāmaṉai yirukkumiṭam nāṭutirēl</l>
<l>atiruṅ kaḻaṟporutō ḷiraṇiya ṉākampi ḷantariyāy</l>
<l>utira maḷaintakaiyō ṭiruntāṉai yuḷḷavākaṇ ṭāruḷar.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If you seek the dwelling place of Rāmā,</l>
<l rend="indent">with uncontested greatness,</l>
<l>he with the tall crown that burns like the rays of a thousand suns,</l>
<l rend="indent">there are those who have seen the truth —</l>
<l>him as a lion, tearing open the chest of Hiraṇya</l>
<l rend="indent">with warring shoulders and shaking anklets,</l>
<l>with hands covered with blood.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
